-- BMW Steps Up Activities in India, Raises Production Capacity in Chennai
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-09-21T07:36:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/bmw-steps-up-activities-in-india-raises-production-capacity-in-chennai.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG is
stepping up its activities in India, raising production capacity
at its plant in Chennai from 3,000 units to 5,400 and further
expanding the dealer network, the company said in an e-mailed
statement today. 